Package org.hibernate.boot.jaxb.mapping.spi

Interface JaxbLifecycleCallbackContainer

All Known Subinterfaces:
JaxbEntity, JaxbEntityOrMappedSuperclass, JaxbMappedSuperclass
All Known Implementing Classes:
JaxbEntityImpl, JaxbEntityListenerImpl, JaxbMappedSuperclassImpl
public interface JaxbLifecycleCallbackContainer
JAXB binding interface for commonality between things which allow callback declarations. This includes
  • entities and mapped-superclasses
  • entity-listener classes
